cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Glimi in your work, please cite it."
title: "Glimi — a living multi-agent harness"
abstract: >-
  A Python harness for a cast of persistent AI characters with their own
  personality, memory, and relationships, that keep going on their own — built
  around a storage/profile/observer-neutral kernel with elastic context budgeting
  and per-character model swapping across cloud and local backends.
type: software
authors:
